CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enter date of 1st attempt made to contact the Claimant. The date first attempt must be a date on or after the creation of the Inactive Record, or no less than 5 days prior to the creation of the Inactive Record. If the first attempt date was made 5 days prior to the creation of the Inactive Record, the Senior deputy can modify the date
CustomField.label: 1st Attempt Date
